ets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝你呀兄弟！</blockquote><br />\n買幾件精緻西餅或者啲中價生果都幾好<br />\n之後就再留意下佢屋企人有咩喜好，就再上時買少少<br />\n<br />\n其次係入屋、食飯叫人，夾餸夾你個方向唔好撈底，盡量有開必答，未食飯果陣問你食唔食飲唔飲，頂多兩塊餅一杯茶，食完飲完主動拎去洗，如被搶話唔洗你做就爭兩野點頭雙手交俾人話唔該。<br />\n<br />\n切記唔好恰眼瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：全部柒過得黎經驗"},{"pid":"01b4dd3226cabae0fe915442bfba43ceda0fb302","tid":166582,"uid":91870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"好似上面巴打講咁，買禮盒囉<br />\n去咩盞記呀果啲鋪頭買個禮盒，嫌貴既就惠康百佳果啲平平地禮盒<br />\n之後同你女朋友打聽佢地一家人平時有無食cake食甜品習慣，買埋上去做飯後甜品<br />\n以上既野有平有貴，咩鋪頭咩價位你自己拿捏啦<br />\n之後上到去不外乎叫人，幫手開台食飯，食完自己拎碗筷入廚房，之後幫手收台扔垃圾果啲老例野。到咁上下時間自己識do走人唔好滾搞人咁耐果啲啦"},{"pid":"925005940c9e60c9e061699bc070fbb092b2cffa","tid":166582,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>簡單啲買西餅  做飯後甜品</blockquote><br />\n好提議！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝你呀兄弟！</blockquote><br />\n祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食過mochi sweet覺得唔錯，臨上去之前會去買。食完飯可以食少少甜野傾下講下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23904586d93c462485be7ace735c354a32bd63c7","tid":166582,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依個post第二個回覆 好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/91260/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/91260/page/1?ref=ios</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0af94d4034ea583a11ecb38650339ee8da22491","tid":166582,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個時第一次上條女屋企食飯，好突然 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩都無準備就上左去，都係注意基本禮貌<br />\n食飯要叫人，開飯前扮下野入廚房問有無野要幫手<br />\n食完又扮下野幫手執野<br />\n通常佢地都會嫌你煩話唔洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢呀媽問定我到時要整咩俾我食，我帶兩梳蕉上去好似唔係咁禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你答咗就預咗以後同佢地食飯都有呢個菜式㗎啦<br />\n所以小心啲揀</blockquote><br />\n我淨係講左唔食海鮮嗰啲（我覺得食魚食蝦嗰啲好麻煩）<br />\n伯母話整雞我食</blockquote><br />\n你以後冇海鮮食</blockquote><br />\n唔緊要我由細到大都麻麻地海鮮"}]}